ji\" />"},{"pid":"c56941f91ad63adc3f160f9a9b469027abbae128","tid":637937,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T14:30:33.000Z","msg":"屌你老母講到自己有開明過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}